metadata.name: The Glooming
metadata.description:
"The Glooming" captures the ethereal and enigmatic essence of the moon. Featuring a blurry and dreamy use of color that evoke a sense of mystery and otherworldliness. Whether through the soft, hazy pastels of a lunar sunrise, or the deep, moody hues of a lunar eclipse, "The Glooming" invites the viewer to lose themselves in the lunar landscape and explore the hidden depths of their imagination. With its immersive and otherworldly visual style, "The Glooming" is a must-have for any fan of abstract art.

Digital art with artificial intelligence.
